<section class="text-center reveal delay-1 md:m-50">
  <h1 class="font-black text-5xl md:text-6xl text-secondary mb-12 pt-8 italic">
    <%= title "Collaborate more, spend less!" %>
  </h1>
  <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-2xl m-0 md:m-20">
    <span class="font-black ">Aïkku CoopComm</span>
    is an inter-municipal resource-sharing platform designed to 
    meet the needs of communities of municipalities,
    inter-municipal associations, and local authorities.
    It supports them in optimizing and pooling
    their human resources, investments, and technical assets within a single tool.
  </h3>
</section>
<div class="footer-wave">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 62" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="
      M0,62
      Q300,2 600,32
      Q900,62 1200,32
      L1200,62
      L0,62
      Z
    " fill="#1f1f3d"/>
  </svg>
</div>
<section id="fonctionnalités" class="w-full text-center bg-info text-white p-10 md:p-20">
  <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-12">
     Everything you need
    <span class="text-gradient">in one place</span>
  </h2>
  <p class="text-center text-[#51c7fd] font-bold text-sm uppercase  mb-16">
    Core features
  </p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-boxes-stacked fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Asset management
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        Track inventory and equipment loans. Manage all usage
        of your assets during field operations. Easily locate your equipment
        using our interactive map.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-screwdriver-wrench fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Operations
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        A service request is submitted by a member to a local team.
        The agent goes on-site, records the information, and the member validates the intervention.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-users fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Agents and managers
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        Agents have limited access to data related to their operations.
        Managers have full access to their organization’s data.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        QR code tracking
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        For recurring operations, create a template intervention and print its QR code.
        By scanning it, the agent directly opens the intervention without manual input.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-euro-sign fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Budget control
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        A management dashboard allows members and managers
        to track key indicators in real time.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-gears fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Workflow
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        Each operation moves from one state to another through predefined actions.
        Some actions automatically trigger notifications.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-message fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Instant messaging
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        A real-time communication space allows managers to directly interact
        with agents, with built-in moderation features.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-bell fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Notifications and alerts
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        Certain state changes trigger email or WhatsApp notifications
        to keep all stakeholders informed.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col p-4 text-left">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-black my-4 underline underline-offset-8 text-white">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-robot fa-lg mr-4 text-[#51c7fd]"></i>
        Intervention forecasting (AI)
      </h3>
      <p class="text-justify text-gray-300">
        Based on previous operations, artificial intelligence
        suggests upcoming interventions to plan.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="footer-wave">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 60" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="M0,0 Q300,60 600,30 Q900,0 1200,30 L1200,0 L0,0 Z" fill="#1f1f3d"/>
  </svg>
</div>
<section class="flex flex-col p-10 md:p-20 md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
  <div class="flex-1 card w-full">
    <%# Replace with your actual dashboard image %>
    <%= image_tag "coopcoomImage.png",
          class: "shadow rounded-2xl",
          alt: "CoopComm dashboard across multiple devices" %>
  </div>
  <div class="flex-1">
    <h3 class="text-lg text-[#51c7fd] font-bold mb-3 text-center md:text-left uppercase tracking-widest">
      Why choose Aïkku CoopComm?     </h3>
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-center md:text-left leading-tight">
      A complete solution to optimize the management of your inter-municipal organization    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-justify text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      A comprehensive solution to optimize the management of your inter-municipal organization by 
      reducing costs, improving team efficiency, ensuring GDPR compliance, 
      and guaranteeing 100% French digital sovereignty.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="footer-wave">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 62" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="
      M0,62
      Q300,2 600,32
      Q900,62 1200,32
      L1200,62
      L0,62
      Z
    " fill="#1f1f3d"/>
  </svg>
</div>
<section class="text-center bg-info text-white px-8 py-16 w-full ">
  <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6">
    Want to see <span class="text-gradient">Aïkku COOPCOMM</span> in action?
  </h2>
  <p class="max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
    Our team offers solutions tailored to your needs,
    with personalized support and technical assistance.
  </p>
  <%= link_to "View the demo →", "https://demo.coopcomm.fr/",
        target: "_blank",
        class: "btn btn-gradient shadow-sm shadow-white/40 mt-6 h-min transition-transform hover:scale-105" %>
</section>
<div class="footer-wave">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 60" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="M0,0 Q300,60 600,30 Q900,0 1200,30 L1200,0 L0,0 Z" fill="#1f1f3d"/>
  </svg>
</div>
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 px-6 md:px-20 mb-20">
  <div class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-xl text-accent group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <i class="fa-brands fa-github fa-2xl"></i>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Development</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black  mb-3">Open source code</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          Developed in France and published with full transparency on 
          <%= link_to "GitHub",
            "https://github.com/philippe-nougaillon/coopcomm",
            target: "_blank",
            class: "font-bold text-accent hover:text-secondary underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4" %>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="group border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl p-8 bg-white shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-xl text-accent group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket fa-2xl"></i>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Support & Services</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-black  mb-3">Need a feature?</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
          Our team is here to support your specific needs.
          <%= link_to services_path, class: "block mt-2 font-semibold text-accent hover:text-secondary transition-colors group/link" do %>
            Explore our custom services offering →
            <span class="block mt-2 font-semibold text-accent cursor-pointer hover:underline">
            </span>
          <% end %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>